            "Ortega Blonde","5.00%","  As the old saying goes“It takes a lot of beer to make good wine.” With this in mindand in collaboration with MuseWinerywe present Ortega Blondea collision of the artisan beer and wine worlds. Freshly crushed Vancouver Island grown Ortega grape juice was fermented along with a Canadian Pilsen based ale resulting in a delicatecomplexeffervescent aleheavy on the citruswith a drywhite wine finish.","On 7 Jan 2015","wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Ortega-Blonde-1024x682.jpg","Spinnakers","Pilsner",
