            "Race Rocks Amber Ale","5.20%","  A blend of the finest specialty malts gives Race Rocks Ale it’s smoothcomplex character and deep chestnut colour.    Don’t let its dark colour scare you; toasted biscuit flavours with subtle notes of caramel and chocolate make Race Rocks an exceptionally mellowwell balanced ale to please any taste.","On 21 Nov 2014","wp-content/uploads/2012/12/racerocks-rebrand-1024x682.jpg","Lighthouse","Amber Ale",
