            "Riptide Pale Ale","5.00%","  Riptide Pale Ale is a full flavouredeasy drinking craft brewed ale with a perfect balance of hop characterand malty smoothness.  The cleancreamy feel and briskfresh flavours awake the taste buds and linger into a drycrispcitrus-noted finish.","On 7 Dec 2012","wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Riptide2-copy-1024x682.jpg","Lighthouse","Pale Ale",
