            "Summer Haze Honey Hefe"," 5.1%"," On a sunny summer dayjust like todaythe Great and Wonderful Oz set sail in his hot-air balloon.  As ballastsome sayhis basket was loaded to the brim with Hoyne Hefeweizen.  After lift-offhis thirst gathered like a summer storm.  Quenching ithe lightened his loadand found himself carried delightfully away.  The restas they sayis his story.","On 16 May 2014","wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Honey-Hefe-1920x1280-1024x682.jpg","Hoyne","Hefeweizen",
